  "detailed_description": "The demons have cursed you! Revenge is your oath and it will lead you down a dangerous path with ever-changing landscapes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800170/extras/e154545684a6eaf7938d4227d915c329.poster.avif?t=1733987087\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800170/extras/e154545684a6eaf7938d4227d915c329.webm?t=1733987087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800170/extras/e154545684a6eaf7938d4227d915c329.mp4?t=1733987087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect relics and cards. Harvest the souls of your enemies. Embrace the potential of your relics by consuming their hidden powers when you face difficult battles. Take risks to reach the final boss and accomplish vengeance. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800170/extras/ed35bfd504d7718da73dcd837b1cc7e2.poster.avif?t=1733987087\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800170/extras/ed35bfd504d7718da73dcd837b1cc7e2.webm?t=1733987087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800170/extras/ed35bfd504d7718da73dcd837b1cc7e2.mp4?t=1733987087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Carefully decide the path you take. Strike any camp in any order. The world changes depending on your choices.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800170/extras/431403bcc11fbf6164caa099f2cb564e.poster.avif?t=1733987087\" widt